{"tid":1123793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州發生2.1級地震 民眾熱議似貨車駛過","createTime":"2019-04-24T16:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T16:31:11.000Z","uid":10385,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c462d3b470814121de8c7c2835d11ad0e3c7174e","tid":1123793,"uid":10385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"據廣州市地震台網正式測定，今天下午3時52分，廣州市增城區(北緯23.20度，東經113.67度)發生2.1級地震，震源深度13公里。<br />\n<br />\n地震在增城區永和、新塘附近普遍有震感，地震沒有造成破壞影響。廣州、東莞網友反饋有震感，紛紛在微博、朋友圈留言，有人表示「還在看書，嚇的腿都軟了！新塘區震感明顯」，有人指「以為有人在樓上蹦」、「以為是大貨車經過」。<br />\n<br />\n廣州市地震局與廣東省地震局專家共同分析後均認為，廣州市後續發生破壞性地震可能性不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986431-中國-廣州發生2.1級地震+民眾熱議似貨車駛過\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986431-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F2.1%E7%B4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%2B%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0%E4%BC%BC%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E9%A7%9B%E9%81%8E&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=f3ad553b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F986431-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F2.1%E7%B4%9A%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%2B%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0%E4%BC%BC%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E9%A7%9B%E9%81%8E&h=28ce981e\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/986431-中國-廣州發生2.1級地震+民眾熱議似貨車駛過</a><br />\n<br />\n唔通個預言係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5e56965d78ec2554574e61d70be85d27e6eaa0","tid":1123793,"uid":9338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1